爆發<br />\n一定冇新case</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"967b95d311d681c7af651aeff2a8a920901d21a5","tid":2072212,"uid":313839,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3360552da3a24ff6deeaad6128d51c4de8bd5f56","tid":2072212,"uid":38164,"like":779,"dislike":5,"score":774,"citedBy":24,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:15:50.000Z","msg":"以為講緊香港北大嶼山醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"真 嚇到我死"},{"pid":"9d1caf12b9094c82c9bf41dde43be4feeea4c63a","tid":2072212,"uid":293848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:16:51.000Z","msg":"頂，個標題嚇死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3d796c9d68b4c8e2164e8c58792d85a79e2118","tid":2072212,"uid":23085,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:17:16.000Z","msg":"寫多兩隻字好似攞佢地條命咁<br />\n係都要兩字式簡化"},{"pid":"e438e485f99459ffcb5d11ef486ff2a32ff4b2d2","tid":2072212,"uid":84116,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d1caf12b9094c82c9bf41dde43be4feeea4c63a","tid":2072212,"uid":293848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:16:51.000Z","msg":"頂，個標題嚇死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:18:16.000Z","msg":"睇到個標題即刻撳入黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b519d35124693f24d7502b9118533d51a04a32","tid":2072212,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4e54100d5c45fd34e037693811f97c7e6420259a","tid":2072212,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3360552da3a24ff6deeaad6128d51c4de8bd5f56","tid":2072212,"uid":38164,"like":779,"dislike":5,"score":774,"ci